  "title": "Corporate Communications Assistant |INX-B01",
  "description": "<p><strong>JOB DESCRIPTION</strong></p><ul><li>Assist in drafting and editing internal and external communications</li><li>Support media monitoring, PR activities, and content distribution</li><li>Help manage social media channels and corporate announcements</li><li>Coordinate with designers and content teams for aligned messaging</li><li>Maintain media lists, press kits, and communication archives</li><li>Support crisis communication preparedness and reputation management</li><li>Assist in organizing corporate events, town halls, or CSR initiatives</li><li>Track communication metrics and prepare summary reports</li></ul><p><strong>JOB REQUIREMENTS</strong></p><ul><li><li>Diploma and above</li><li>Training will be provided</li></li><li>Excellent written and verbal communication skills</li><li>Detail-oriented and able to maintain brand voice consistency</li><li>Interest in media, public relations, and corporate storytelling</li></ul><p><strong>EA License Number: 25C2980</strong></p><p><strong>Disclaimer:</strong></p><p>By applying, you consent to the collection and use of your personal data for recruitment purposes in accordance with Singapore’s PDPA. Your application may be considered for this and other suitable roles.</p>",
